{
  "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "一个赌徒带着一笔本金走进赌场，心里盘算着翻倍就收手。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.54,
      "size": 24624,
      "text": "他要么先输光离场，要么先达到目标金额。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "问题是：这两种结局，各自会以多大的概率降临？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.43,
      "size": 22896,
      "text": "这就是概率论里著名的赌徒破产问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "walk",
      "line_id": "walk-1",
      "filename": "walk-walk-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/walk-walk-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "每赌一局，资金就上下跳动一元，像在数轴上左右随机迈步。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "walk",
      "line_id": "walk-2",
      "filename": "walk-walk-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/walk-walk-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "资金触到零就破产，触到目标就达标，这是两道吸收壁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "walk",
      "line_id": "walk-3",
      "filename": "walk-walk-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/walk-walk-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "只要一直玩下去，游走终究会撞上其中一道壁停下。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-1",
      "filename": "formula-form-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/formula-form-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "若每局输赢机会均等，破产概率就是目标减本金再除以目标。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-2",
      "filename": "formula-form-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/formula-form-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "换句话说，本金占目标的比例越小，破产的可能就越大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-3",
      "filename": "formula-form-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/formula-form-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "若胜率不到一半，则要用输赢比的幂次公式来精确计算。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "fairness",
      "line_id": "fair-1",
      "filename": "fairness-fair-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/fairness-fair-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "公平赌局里，破产与达标的概率恰好由本金和目标的比例决定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "fairness",
      "line_id": "fair-2",
      "filename": "fairness-fair-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/fairness-fair-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "可一旦胜率哪怕只低了一两个百分点，破产概率就急剧攀升。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "fairness",
      "line_id": "fair-3",
      "filename": "fairness-fair-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/fairness-fair-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "赌场正是靠这点微小而稳定的优势，让长期玩家几乎必输。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "切换不同赌局设置，调整本金与胜率，看多局轨迹奔向哪道壁。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "点击重新模拟，对照理论破产概率，感受红绿两色的此消彼长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "赌徒破产，是一场带两道吸收壁的随机游走。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "公平时看本金比例，不公平时那点劣势会被无限放大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gamblers-ruin",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gamblers-ruin/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "数学早已告诉我们久赌必输的道理，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 37.17,
  "total_size": 594864
}